For the Ludlow family: William Seton Gordon, 
                Gabriel Ludlow (1663-1736) and his descendants (call number CS71.L8465.1919); 
                Proceedings at the laying of the corner-stone of the Ludlow and Willink Hall of St. Stephen's College, Annandale, N.Y. on Wednesday, June 13, A.D. 1866 (call number CS71.L8465.1866). (St. Stephen's College is now Bard College and the Ludlow-Willink Hall is used as its main administration building.)
